此高架車站於1908年8月1日啟用<ref>{{cite news|title=Our First Subway Completed At Last: Opening of the Van Cortlandt Extension Finishes System Begun in 1900|url=http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9E06E1DB113EE033A25751C0A96E9C946997D6CF|accessdate=2015-08-16|publisher=New York Times|date=1908-08-02|archive-date=2016-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160409012005/http://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive-free/pdf?res=9E06E1DB113EE033A25751C0A96E9C946997D6CF|dead-url=no}}</ref>，設有兩個[[側式月台|側式月台]]和三條軌道，中央軌道不營運。1948年7月9日，此站的月台延長至514英呎，容許10節列車停靠，之前只可停靠6節列車。此月台延長工程為一個[[IRT百老匯-第七大道線|IRT百老匯-第七大道線]]5個車站月台延長工程計劃的一部分，共計423,000萬美元<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9F0CE4D7123EE03BBC4852DFB1668383659EDE|title=MORE LONG PLATFORMS; Five Subway Stations on IRT to Accommodate 10-Car Trains|date=1948-07-10|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-03-27|archive-date=2016-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408204234/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9F0CE4D7123EE03BBC4852DFB1668383659EDE|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

由於此站向北距離總站只有一個車站，距離較短，因此北行月台只限下車<ref>{{cite web|title=MTA Neighborhood Maps: Riverdale|url=http://web.mta.info/maps/neighborhoods/bx/BX3_Riverdale_2015.pdf|website=[[大都會運輸署|mta.info]]|publisher=[[大都會運輸署|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|accessdate=2015-09-15|date=2015|archive-date=2020-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605043809/http://web.mta.info/maps/neighborhoods/bx/BX3_Riverdale_2015.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

